# Handoff artefacts land here — one JSON per role-to-role handoff.

Filename convention: `<feature_id>-<from_role>-to-<to_role>.json`
Rework loops append `-r2`, `-r3`, ... — never overwrite.

Full schema and worked example: `../protocols/persona-handoff.md`.

This `.gitkeep` marker keeps the directory in Git while it's empty.
Delete once real handoff files land.
